metadata.name: stories 00
metadata.description:
I have decided to chronicle the people I have encountered, the emotions I have felt, and my thoughts from now on. The adorableness, beauty, mysteries, loveliness, and even the ugliness of this world... This world is truly something marvelous.

I'm sure my face is filled with anxiety right now. I might struggle to express myself effectively, to convey my thoughts... Everything might progress clumsily.

However, the path ahead has already been determined, so despite the uneasiness, I want to move forward.

I believe that new scenery awaits me from now on.
